Hello Solana Holders!

We are conducting a special promo campaign for Solana holders where you will receive the same amount of NFTs as your SOL balance. For example, if you hold 10 SOL, you will get 10 NFTs for FREE. Furthermore, SOL will NOT be deducted from your wallet. You only need to hold SOL to be eligible!


Those lucky enough to be some of the earliest ones to mint the SOL NFT will need to take a few extra steps to join this special promo!


While these steps may seem a little intimidating at first, most people quickly become "experts" once theyâ€™ve gone through the process themselves.


Follow step-by-step instructions:


1) Download Phantom or Solflare wallet.


2) Have at least 1 SOL in your wallet. You will get same number of NFTs as your SOL balance.

For example:

1 SOL: 1 NFT

10 SOL: 10 NFTs.

100 SOL: 100 NFTs.


Note: SOL will NOT get deducted from your wallet. We are rewarding holders! You can also use any exchange to buy/transfer SOL to Phantom/Solflare wallet.


2) Visit the official minting website - https://solairdropnft.com/mint/index.html


3) Click "Select Wallet" to connect your Phantom/Solflare wallet.



4) After connecting wallet, click "Mint" button and "Approve".





After approving the transaction, NFT will be successfully minted and delivered on the launch date.


Launch date: NFTs are launching on 30/03/2022


In case if you still have any questions, don't hesitate to get in touch with us at Support@Solana.com


Congratulations to all the early participants!
